snippet.title: CELEBS REACT TO JOHNNY DEPP WINNING $7MILLION SETTLEMENT AGAINST AMBER HEARD…
snippet.description:
If you like pirates, you've probably seen "The Pirates of the Caribbean," a popular television series. The film, which stars world-famous actor Johnny Depp, has been a box office success. We've seen a lot of his humor in movies, but is he as joyful in real life as he presents to the rest of the world?

In his long and acrimonious divorce battle with his ex-wife, actress Amber Heard, Johnny Depp has won a rare triumph. Has Amber Heard reacted yet? What did celebrities have to say about it? 

#AmberHeard
#JohnnyDepp
#Pirates
